OL,3,CWales tourism tax plans outlined as
OL,4,Cvisitors may be charged #1.25 a day
OL,6,FIt's estimated that the levy could
OL,7,Fbring in as much as #33million per
OL,8,Fyear if every Welsh local authority
OL,9,Fwere to introduce it.
OL,11,FSupporters say the change will raise
OL,12,Fmoney to pay for vital services,
OL,13,Finfrastructure and to help offset the
OL,14,Fimpact of tourists in popular areas.
OL,16,FOpponents say that it will discourage
OL,17,Fvisitors and cost tourism businesses
OL,18,Fin lost revenue and increased red tape.
