OL,3,CWales tourism tax plans outlined as
OL,4,Cvisitors may be charged #1.25 a day
OL,6,FAny change won't come into effect for
OL,7,Fat least three years. Firstly, Senedd
OL,8,FMembers have to vote to change the law
OL,9,Fand then any local council which
OL,10,Fwanted to introduce a charge would
OL,11,Fhave to carry out a consultation and
OL,12,Fwait 12 months. It means the earliest
OL,13,Fthat any visitor levy would be charged
OL,14,Fwould be 2027.
OL,16,FIt's also thought that not every
OL,17,Fcouncil would want to introduce a
OL,18,Fvisitor levy.
