OL,6,FHowever, once a local authority has
OL,7,Fintroduced it, they would be able to
OL,8,Fraise the charge by as much as they
OL,9,Fsee fit, subject to further
OL,10,Fconsultation and a possible cap
OL,11,Fimposed by Welsh ministers.
OL,13,FVisitor levies are used in many parts
OL,14,Fof the world, including Manchester,
OL,15,FGreece, Germany, Netherlands, Spain,
OL,16,FPortugal and California.
