OL,6,FAny Welsh council charging the visitor
OL,7,Flevy would have to publish a report
OL,8,Fabout how the money is spent, proving
OL,9,Fthat it was used for the purposes
OL,10,Fintended.
OL,12,FUnder the proposals, certain groups
OL,13,Fwill be exempt from paying the levy or
OL,14,Fcan claim refunds, such as homeless
OL,15,Fpeople placed in hotels and those who
OL,16,Fare forced to stay in hotels because
OL,17,Fof emergencies like fire or flooding.
