OL,6,FThe Welsh Government is expected to
OL,7,Fpublish an economic impact assessment
OL,8,Falongside the legislation which will
OL,9,Fset out potential positive, negative
OL,10,Fand neutral effects of the change.
OL,12,FWales' finance secretary Mark
OL,13,FDrakeford said: "This Bill is rooted
OL,14,Fin the principle of fairness. We know
OL,15,Ftourism makes an important
OL,16,Fcontribution to the Welsh economy and
OL,17,Fto Welsh life. We want to ensure its
OL,18,Flong-term sustainability.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
