OL,3,CWales tourism tax plans outlined as
OL,4,Cvisitors may be charged #1.25 a day
OL,6,F"That's why we believe it is fair
OL,7,Fvisitors contribute towards local
OL,8,Ffacilities, helping to fund
OL,9,Finfrastructure and services integral
OL,10,Fto their experience. Visitor levies
OL,11,Fare common around the world,
OL,12,Fbenefiting local communities, tourists
OL,13,Fand businesses ` and we want the same
OL,14,Ffor Wales.
OL,16,F"Money raised through a levy would be
OL,17,Fretained by local authorities and re-
OL,18,Finvested back into their local areas
OL,19,Fto support local, sustainable tourism.
OL,20,FIt's a small contribution that could
OL,21,Fmake a big difference."
