OL,6,FA statutory registration scheme for
OL,7,Fall accommodation providers is
OL,8,Fexpected to start operating in 2026 to
OL,9,Fsupport the collection and
OL,10,Fadministration of a visitor levy.
OL,12,FCouncillor Andrew Morgan OBE, Welsh
OL,13,FLocal Government Association leader,
OL,14,Fsaid: "This Bill will give councils
OL,15,Fthe option to introduce a visitor levy
OL,16,Fon overnight stays. It's a way to
OL,17,Fraise extra funds to support local
OL,18,Fservices and improve amenities that
OL,19,Fbenefit both visitors and the
OL,20,Fcommunity.
