OL,4,Cvisitors may be charged #1.25 a day
OL,6,FWelsh Conservatives' Peter Fox MS,
OL,7,Fshadow minister for finance and local
OL,8,Fgovernment, said: "We've been
OL,9,Fabsolutely clear from the start that
OL,10,Fthis policy is the wrong one for
OL,11,FWales. A tourism tax will risk jobs at
OL,12,Fa time when businesses are being
OL,13,Fclobbered by Labour, it will impose
OL,14,Fred tape, and it will work against its
OL,15,Fown aims by encouraging visitors to
OL,16,Fuse more council-maintained
OL,17,Fattractions and services. Our tourism
OL,18,Findustry should be nurtured by the
OL,19,FWelsh Government, not hamstrung by new
OL,20,Ftaxes."
